citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 4:15 PM on 15
March 2023. Called facility representative and left a message, waited over an hour at the facility then called and left
another message with no response.
End Section
